# Repository Stability

A guide to understanding the maturity and support level of repositories in the Glean organization.

---

![Experimental](https://img.shields.io/badge/-Experimental-D8FD49?style=flat-square&logo=data:image/svg+xml;base64,&labelColor=343CED)

Early-stage exploration. Use at your own risk.

- Active development with frequent breaking changes
- APIs, interfaces, and functionality may change without notice
- Limited or no documentation
- No support guarantees
- Not recommended for production use

---

![Alpha](https://img.shields.io/badge/-Alpha-D8FD49?style=flat-square&logo=data:image/svg+xml;base64,&labelColor=343CED)

Initial testing phase. Core functionality works but incomplete.

- Major features still in development
- Breaking changes expected between releases
- Basic documentation available
- Community support only
- Suitable for early adopters and internal testing

---

![Beta](https://img.shields.io/badge/-Beta-D8FD49?style=flat-square&logo=data:image/svg+xml;base64,&labelColor=343CED)

Feature-complete but still maturing.

- All major features implemented
- Breaking changes possible but communicated in advance
- Documentation complete
- Limited support available
- Suitable for non-critical production use

---

![Prerelease](https://img.shields.io/badge/-Prerelease-FFFFFF?style=flat-square&logo=data:image/svg+xml;base64,&labelColor=343CED)

Final validation before general availability.

- Feature-complete and stable
- No breaking changes expected
- Full documentation and examples
- Support available
- Suitable for production with awareness of pending GA

---

![Enterprise Ready](https://img.shields.io/badge/-Enterprise%20Ready-FFFFFF?style=flat-square&logo=data:image/svg+xml;base64,&labelColor=343CED)

Production-grade and fully supported.

- Stable APIs with semantic versioning
- Breaking changes only in major versions with migration guides
- Comprehensive documentation
- Full enterprise support through Glean support channels
- Security reviewed and performance validated
